#

Honey Chipotle Shrimp Tacos

$15.99
540 kcal
Difficulty: 50%

Allergens:

shellfishdairy

Dietary Tags:

glutenFreehighProteinlowCarb

Tags:

tacosseafoodspicyMexican

Description

Spicy and sweet shrimp served in soft corn tortillas, topped with a tangy slaw.

Ingredients

  • shrimp: 1 lb
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • honey: 2 tbsp
  • chipotle pepper in adobo sauce: 1-2
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • avocado: 1
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
